Central European Media Hits 2 1/2-Month High on Acquisition

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-03-28T15:32:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/central-european-media-hits-2-month-high-on-bontonfilm-takeover.html
Central European Media Enterprises
Ltd. (CETV)  jumped to its highest in 2 1/2 months after the broadcaster
said it agreed to purchase Bontonfilm AS, a Czech distributor of
films and television programs.  The stock advanced 2.2 percent to 371 koruna by 4:24 p.m.
in  Prague , its highest close since Jan. 12, extending its gains
so far this month to 7.5 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
 kchamonikola@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at   gserkin@bloomberg.net  